\s1 Avoiding favouritism
\p
\v 1 My dear brothers and sisters, as you live out your faith¦147906 in our honoured master¦147908 Jesus the messiah¦147911, don't show favouritism¦147903 to others.
\v 2 For \add example\add*, if a man in nicely cut clothes and wearing an expensive gold¦147922 ring came into to your meeting as well as a poor man in filthy¦147931 clothes
